snippet.title: Axiom Verge 2 - Official Xbox Launch Trailer | ID@Xbox Showcase
snippet.description:
Axiom Verge 2, as well as Axiom Verge, is available now on Xbox. Check out the latest trailer for another look at the sci-fi world and aliens you'll encounter in this side-scrolling action-exploration game.

#IGN #Gaming #Xbox
